This is a validations presentation plan

1. Activerecord validations

2. Verify.js
	+ easy to use
	+ layout is OK
	+ ajax validation
	- i have no idea how to customize basic rules
	- lib is very fat - ~40kb

3. Validate.js
	+ lib is very soft ~ 3kb
	- no inline alerts
	- no useful syntax
	- no ajax validation
	- looks like activerecord validation

4. HTML Form Validation
	+ easy to use
	- no customize - it is HTML5 features

5. VALIDATE.JS
	
